OL,11,FWho was Lady Rhondda?
OL,13,FLady Rhondda was born Margaret Haig
OL,14,FThomas in 1883.
OL,16,FShe was a suffragette, spearheading
OL,17,Fthe campaign for votes for women in
OL,18,FNewport.
OL,20,FShe set fire to a postbox that still
OL,21,Fstands on Risca Road in Newport.
